basic.Peptide Name: Skin peptide tyrosine-tyrosine (Skin-PYY; SPYY; Frogs, amphibians, animals)
basic.Target Organism: Gram-negative bacteria:Aeromonas caviae (MIC=40 µg/ml), Escherichia coli (MIC=10 µg/ml);Gram-positive bacteria:Enterococcus faecalis (MIC=10 µg/ml), Nocardia brasiliensis (MIC=20 µg/ml).Fungi:Cryptococcus neoformans (MIC=20 µg/ml), Candida albicans (MIC=15 µg/ml), Microsporum canis (MIC=10 µg/ml), Tricophyton rubrum (MIC=15 µg/ml), Arthroderma simii (MIC=10 µg/ml), Aspergillus fumigatus (MIC=80 µg/ml), Aspergillus niger (MIC>100 µg/ml).
